  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/f1af2436af8fe32753963c7824e4dc82.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br>You have just become the proud new owner of a fertile square field. Can you master the skill of square farming and earn yourself a bountiful, quadrangular harvest?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/516564e5942b4e87a58482272fecbb8d.poster.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/516564e5942b4e87a58482272fecbb8d.webm?t=1721293943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/516564e5942b4e87a58482272fecbb8d.mp4?t=1721293943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>What is square farming you ask? It's simple! Plant your weirdly shaped blocks of seeds somewhere in your big, square field. If you fill a row, column, or 3x3 square, the crop is harvested! Harvest multiple times at once, and your crops will be a better quality!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/fe2092e374daa736f61f4ff477bfa9c4.poster.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/fe2092e374daa736f61f4ff477bfa9c4.webm?t=1721293943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/fe2092e374daa736f61f4ff477bfa9c4.mp4?t=1721293943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Farm your way through the year, and as you do, you'll unlock new crops, each with their own unique shape and values. Which four crops do you want to use today? The trickier the crop, the more money you'll earn! Aim for your best score!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/1f07690ef5b8e479f8abbc3e22003d9b.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br>Every once in a while, you'll be visited by a local from the nearby town of Squarewood!<br><br>Befriend, date or marry one of the villagers, each with their own unique story. Who will you get to know first?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/a0f1240f38804fa04a312a76e056c0e0.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/2b1a96e708ea9eaaa829d9ca1acaed20.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/5aa26364ac29dfc495235905134466c0.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/2df24d1750a7d7bf69d2685145ab16b8.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/a311b9ae75f345475e51c5d2c7f94070.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/cc7f4ce71db54d491edb85682402d044.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade your farm with new buildings tools! A barn? A watering can? A mayonnaise maker?<br></li><li>Squarewood Town is just around the corner. Hop on your bike and give the village a visit!<br></li><li>Enjoy each villager's unique story and even go on romantic dates!<br></li><li>Take a break from farming and go fishing for the day instead!<br></li><li>Animals! Animals can be used to farm animal products instead of crops.<br></li><li>Adopt a cat or dog to keep you company while you farm!<br></li><li>Customize your farm with different fences and houses!<br></li><li>Watch the season change as you progress through the year. Plant the right crop in the right season to earn bonuses.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/f1af2436af8fe32753963c7824e4dc82.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br>You have just become the proud new owner of a fertile square field. Can you master the skill of square farming and earn yourself a bountiful, quadrangular harvest?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/516564e5942b4e87a58482272fecbb8d.poster.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/516564e5942b4e87a58482272fecbb8d.webm?t=1721293943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/516564e5942b4e87a58482272fecbb8d.mp4?t=1721293943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>What is square farming you ask? It's simple! Plant your weirdly shaped blocks of seeds somewhere in your big, square field. If you fill a row, column, or 3x3 square, the crop is harvested! Harvest multiple times at once, and your crops will be a better quality!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/fe2092e374daa736f61f4ff477bfa9c4.poster.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/fe2092e374daa736f61f4ff477bfa9c4.webm?t=1721293943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/fe2092e374daa736f61f4ff477bfa9c4.mp4?t=1721293943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Farm your way through the year, and as you do, you'll unlock new crops, each with their own unique shape and values. Which four crops do you want to use today? The trickier the crop, the more money you'll earn! Aim for your best score!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/1f07690ef5b8e479f8abbc3e22003d9b.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br>Every once in a while, you'll be visited by a local from the nearby town of Squarewood!<br><br>Befriend, date or marry one of the villagers, each with their own unique story. Who will you get to know first?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/a0f1240f38804fa04a312a76e056c0e0.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/2b1a96e708ea9eaaa829d9ca1acaed20.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/5aa26364ac29dfc495235905134466c0.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/2df24d1750a7d7bf69d2685145ab16b8.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/a311b9ae75f345475e51c5d2c7f94070.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=110 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830450/extras/cc7f4ce71db54d491edb85682402d044.avif?t=1721293943\" width=600 height=90 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade your farm with new buildings tools! A barn? A watering can? A mayonnaise maker?<br></li><li>Squarewood Town is just around the corner. Hop on your bike and give the village a visit!<br></li><li>Enjoy each villager's unique story and even go on romantic dates!<br></li><li>Take a break from farming and go fishing for the day instead!<br></li><li>Animals! Animals can be used to farm animal products instead of crops.<br></li><li>Adopt a cat or dog to keep you company while you farm!<br></li><li>Customize your farm with different fences and houses!<br></li><li>Watch the season change as you progress through the year. Plant the right crop in the right season to earn bonuses.</li></ul>",
